  shape: rectangle
}

EmailSystem: |md
  ## 邮件系统
  [外部系统]

  提供通知服务
| {
  shape: rectangle
}

User -> BlogSystem.SubscriptionContext: "订阅"
BlogSystem.SubscriptionContext -> BlogSystem.NotificationContext: "事件通知"
BlogSystem.NotificationContext -> EmailSystem: "反馈"
EmailSystem -> User: "通知"




